item.dc:creator: @kickingjamie kickingjamie
item.description:
@kickingjamie wrote:

Why is it that all videos like this have someone shouting with an annoying echo and some music that nobody understands? Surely they are trying to target people who are not from that country and probably don’t speak Arabic - in other words people who are not from 3rd world countries like syria. Therefore they should use voice and music that the target audience understand? Because honestly… Who likes reading subtitles???
